R22 Costa crash was a custom bitlife event taking place on March 4th, 1981. Featuring just 1 death, with only [[Filipe Costa]]. It was a accident which still cant not be solved till this day. In this page you will be through the time-lapse of Filipes last moments before he passed.

== Time-lapse ==
8:30am: Filipe, went to take his helicopter for a ride, not knowing the danger of riding it during this time.

8:45am: he arrived and prepared for the flight, trying to put for safety cautions.

8:56am: he went into his helicopter flying it soaring into the air.

9:10am: He noticed a flock of birds, in his way while flying his R22 Robinson. He tried getting them out of the way but it made it worse as it hit the edge of the helicopter.

9:12am: He was terrified as it yawed dangerously back and forth, as he tried spinning it to get back to the air, screaming help.

9:14am: He quickly tried to find a way to escape his helicopter, also as well trying to call for help and got ahold of his wife.

9:16am: He screamed he needed help, as the plane tall spinning almost reaching the ground, he told them the exact address.

9:18am: He, screamed help as the plane crashed, unfortunately he passed away due to the accident.
